spell = Spell.create(name: "Plant Growth", level: 3, school_id: transmutation.id, casting_time: "1 action or 8 hours", range: "150 feet", duration: "Instantaneous", short_description: "1a: 100-ft rad plants overgrow for 1/4 speed; 8h: 1 mile diameter plants yield double food at harvest", description: "This spell channels vitality into plants within a specific area. There are two possible uses for the spell, granting either immediate or long-term benefits. If you cast this spell using 1 action, choose a point within range. All normal plants in a 100-foot radius centered on that point become thick and overgrown. A creature moving through the area must spend 4 feet of movement for every 1 foot it moves. You can exclude one or more areas of any size within the spell's area from being affected. If you cast this spell over 8 hours, you enrich the land. All plants in a half-mile radius centered on a point within range become enriched for 1 year. The plants yield twice the normal amount of food when harvested.", v: true, s: true, m: false, r: false)
